{"tid":1192069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果日報：遇到有武器人士／暴力衝擊，保持距離，拿出手機拍攝再向糾察報告情況！","createTime":"2019-06-08T08:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T23:07:24.000Z","uid":202698,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"34f34ea8d4c783dbaf6eade035d9eee2c8f1cca9","tid":1192069,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190608/59690990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190608%2F59690990&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSYpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=72d0594e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190608%2F59690990&h=85f1fc81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190608/59690990</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣發起6.9「反送中」大遊行前夕，前特首梁振英借昨天的2宗汽油彈事件，暗指汽油彈襲擊與部份人「政治利益」有關，借勢再斥「違法達義」行動不當，而每逢民主派舉行大型遊行，警方以及愛字堆總以種種方法阻撓與挑釁。目的為何？相信港人心中有數。為免和平理性遊行因此受破壞，撐傘落區運動在Facebook發帖，以6點【溫馨提示】，呼籲遊行市民勿中計！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6點溫馨提示<br />\n1）<span style=\"color: red;\">若有人起哄，保持警覺，理性先行</span>，了解事態先行動，不要道聽途說、以情緒行動（激動）；<br />\n<br />\n2）<span style=\"color: red;\">有人做出暴力衝擊，不要上前參與，拿出手機，保持距離，拍攝現場情況</span>。用鏡頭保護示威者，令警察保持克制；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）面對警方刁難，保持平靜心境，不中警察激將法，（要知遊行時間越長越好）反利用其刁難，留守街道；可能的話因應情況，與附近同伴商討能否有空間共同坐下休息（請大家帶方便櫈）；<br />\n<br />\n4）<span style=\"color: red;\">若遇有武器人士，立即與他們拉開距離，找尋遊行糾察報告情況</span>；<br />\n<br />\n5）遊行中可能有警民僵持情況，在警民之間，大家特別留意「第3至7排」人士，<span style=\"color: red;\">小心有人惡意投擲東西向警方，故意挑起警方向人群展開行動。遇有情況，遊行人士同速同聲叫「唔好掟嘢、停止掟嘢」</span>，不要俾警察有藉口行動；<br />\n<br />\n6）有人指罵遊行人士時，唔好同佢嘈，如有人忍唔住同佢對罵，唔好叫佢 「冷靜」，因為佢聽到會覺得同路人指責佢，可以講：「條友真係衰（認同佢感受），<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好理佢，想攪亂我地（哋），唔好中計。</span>」然後陪佢遠離。"},{"pid":"e26e6a5be62084782d011ccba73b611dd68bc211","tid":1192069,"uid":188411,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"唉屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"8b705ffa7fd610f4fa384c8dcbe98133b5d5f8e5","tid":1192069,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d7277878d907d572d4e48b617d285bb99a768d","tid":1192069,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b096f2a19574397dd6762c8132b82f38750b49ca","tid":1192069,"uid":76591,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"毒果，關鍵時刻教人督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2613dda74075b19bc25febe49e8e327b0d5759f","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"邊個比錢蘋果日報, 邊個就係鬼"},{"pid":"2dcf9bbc52b7e7cd349f80960098a56b7135cdd9","tid":1192069,"uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報收錢一堆人話比錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf073c70f299610779381a22519d2a6721529ba","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2dcf9bbc52b7e7cd349f80960098a56b7135cdd9","tid":1192069,"uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報收錢一堆人話比錢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"成班都ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20c224d8c687c457d9e0d760754971402b607c2","tid":1192069,"uid":74058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"會行使公民拘捕<br />\n拘捕相關人等 交俾警方"},{"pid":"3e3dcb0371aefbad04f32ce81dd4b6265397c26a","tid":1192069,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"分撚完化未呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"0ef6eadf29fa3b769896abaa3d78650cf1a3cadb","tid":1192069,"uid":119478,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"理性呢個字真係無敵<br />\n有時仲難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523eafcb8b7305dc9e6b6e64fc7f0bd8a609cde2","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e20c224d8c687c457d9e0d760754971402b607c2","tid":1192069,"uid":74058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"會行使公民拘捕<br />\n拘捕相關人等 交俾警方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地係一直COPY 8964 篤灰北京學生既仆街行為</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/19/admin/cn-liusi1/cn-liusi1-jumbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2Fadmin%2Fcn-liusi1%2Fcn-liusi1-jumbo.jpg&h=7e0f0c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1989年春天，北京爆發了一場聲勢浩大的民主運動。當年5月23日下午兩點，三位來自毛澤東家鄉湖南的年輕人余志堅、喻東嶽、魯德成，在天安門城樓下打出一幅大橫幅：「五千年專制就此告一段落，個人崇拜從此可以休矣」，隨後用裝上顏料的雞蛋投擲塗污天安門城樓上的毛澤東畫像。<br />\n三人的行為讓廣場上一直和平抗議的學生感到很意外。之後，三人被廣場上維持秩序的學生糾察隊扣留，後轉交給北京市公安機關處理。<br />\n是時，余志堅25歲，為瀏陽一名小學教師；喻東嶽22歲，為《瀏陽日報》美術編輯；魯德成26歲，為瀏陽汽車運輸公司修理工。同年8月11日，魯德成、喻東嶽分別被北京市中級人民法院以「反革命破壞」和「反革命煽動」等罪名判處16年有期徒刑和20年有期徒刑；作為主謀，余志堅被判無期徒刑。他們成為中國成千上萬的六四政治犯中判刑較重的三位。<br />\n1998年，魯德成獲假釋出獄；2004年8月，他離開中國，經緬甸偷渡到泰國，並向聯合國難民署尋求庇護；2006年4月，他以難民身份進入加拿大，獲得永久居留權。2000年9月，余志堅經減刑，獲假釋出獄。2006年2月喻東嶽獲得減刑出獄，但已經精神失常，出獄後由余志堅照顧其生活。2008年4月底，余志堅攜妻子和喻東嶽及他妹妹喻日霞偷渡至泰國，一年後獲得庇護抵達美國。"},{"pid":"1ed60dcd4a8c9eb9763a712d25205274c32d4a44","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef6eadf29fa3b769896abaa3d78650cf1a3cadb","tid":1192069,"uid":119478,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"理性呢個字真係無敵<br />\n有時仲難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"行完沙圈就散, 年復一年咁行, 得個桔<br />\n先至係最無理性既行為"},{"pid":"1531386e6f1b8de3cae4acf6477733f74868c5fb","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"係咪應該將泛民糾察視為敵人?"},{"pid":"0da093e0503d794769bb62f6936cd7d3a04a81fc","tid":1192069,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"如有警察/ 暴力衝擊，屌佢老母臭化閪，<br />\n用手機影畀各國領事"},{"pid":"bb43babf0a97051da62ab1b55fc90182570e4c78","tid":1192069,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n各有各做<br />\n屌泛民等於分化<br />\n唔好模糊69焦點<br />\n遊行人數少對邊個最有利<br />\n團結次要敵人"},{"pid":"d19048c8182e20cfa357d65d3bfb1a06f72d0bb8","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人做出暴力衝擊，不要上前參與，拿出手機，保持距離，拍攝現場情況。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁多事, 唔驚機都打爆你?"},{"pid":"a7113031984f5de917c8b73ba9430f2dea042da2","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"世上有3種人：<br />\n(1) 做嘢既人<br />\n(2) 唔做嘢既人<br />\n(3) 阻住人做嘢既人"},{"pid":"987230ce1f7af11eba599b657363907097a1f78f","tid":1192069,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4803df4d991309ca7dd8514da44e683f8a51c71e","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb43babf0a97051da62ab1b55fc90182570e4c78","tid":1192069,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n各有各做<br />\n屌泛民等於分化<br />\n唔好模糊69焦點<br />\n遊行人數少對邊個最有利<br />\n團結次要敵人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係各有各做喎<br />\n<br />\n係白紙黑字, 叫人篤灰, 阻住你做喎"},{"pid":"20048468272ddee5d5ee768ab1b131ded952cdfe","tid":1192069,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\n不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ec7ed1da4fd37392e93bebc0d84b27e2181b0c","tid":1192069,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4762a546d2d5cb6f51f5c404fd9a66646adba16","tid":1192069,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"聽日舉行和理非非假膠嘉年華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc193555d05685a62913a8a18067001da3e34ba","tid":1192069,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"真心唔建議大家衝<br />\n<br />\n一衝就比人報串，然後比人拉"},{"pid":"fd93629539053f3fb70c7865ca013796c5e8bb0a","tid":1192069,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc193555d05685a62913a8a18067001da3e34ba","tid":1192069,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"真心唔建議大家衝<br />\n<br />\n一衝就比人報串，然後比人拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"最終解決辦法, 都係要拆咗大台先?"}]}